<br>
With that said, what I'm about to say isnt going to make some people happy. I'm sure most monks aren't going to like what I have to say, but I'm pretty sure no one else gives a crap. But like I said, I'm honest, and honesty and fairness means more to me than not upsetting people.<br>
<br>
So I might as well say it: my 35 Human Monk is extremely overpowered. Okay, so I'm talking a fungi-tunicced, 19/20 2hb staffed, SoS hasted from my epic 60 ench on another account, but nevertheless, she is way way way too broken.<br>
<br>
Let me paint a picture so you understand. Today in Guk, I was soloing stuff with SoS on. I'd like pull, beat the shiz out of mob while regening all damage from fungi during the fight, and continue. I had like no downtime, except every 20 minutes to run to zonein for my SoS click. I was like &quot;OMG, this is pure roxor, I cannot die!&quot;<br>
<br>
Now, I know what your thinking. &quot;your only level 35, fungis arent as good at higher levels!&quot; Well, here's a liddle secret- I have this skill called instill doubt to fear stuff and not take dmg! So I can still solo nonstop! And if I do manage to get  seriously hurt, I have a skill called mend, meaning I get free health! At over 100 skill, it never fails! And if somehow, during those high level pulls, it still goes bad, I can feign death like a necro or sk, only it has no cast time, and succeeds 99% of the time, making it nigh impossible to kill me!<br>
<br>
Why am I saying this? Mostly my concience. When I'm killing stuff in &lt;insert zone here&gt; twice as fast as any other soloer, including the idiot chanter with the hasted pet, I feel bad. I feel bad that I can kill non-stop with no risk and negligible downtime. And how can i be able to do this? 'Cause of a liddle thing called a Fungi Tunic. Also, cause of my class skills as a monk. Also, cause I have such ubar weapons I can get. So really, the problem here isnt that monks themselves are inherently overpowered; thats just part of it. When you throw in all the stuff they can use, tho....They become gods.<br>
<br>
So, in conclusion, I believe monks need to have all weapon skills max out at 10 skill, remove FD and mend as class skills, and make them unable to equip any weapons. Then they will be balanced, and the game will be fair to all again. Then my conscience will be at east.<br>
<br>
Thanks! <p>Dexanth Dragonborne <BR>

